commit.message:
Added enable_pec to Enable/Disable PEC (#53)

* Added enable_pec to Enable/Disable PEC

Added member function enable_pec to SMBus to Enable/Disable PEC (Packet Error Checking, see SMBus 1.1 and later).

Example:
    bus=smbus2.SMBus(1)
    bus.enable_pec()

* Added pec property as a drop-in replacement for smbus field

- Added property pec (setter only). Now the old interface is available as: bus.pec=1
- Documented member function parameters
- Changed ValueError to IOError
